---
import BaseLayout from './BaseLayout.astro';
const { frontmatter } = Astro.props;
---
<BaseLayout title={`${frontmatter.title}｜Rose Lab`} description={frontmatter.description}>
  <div class="wrap article-shell">
    <article class="article-main">
      <header class="article-header">
        <span class="category">{frontmatter.category}</span>
        <h1>{frontmatter.title}</h1>
        <p class="article-description">{frontmatter.description}</p>
        <div class="article-meta">發布日期：{frontmatter.pubDate.toLocaleDateString('zh-TW')}</div>
      </header>
      <div class="article-notice">本文記錄我們家的實際使用經驗，不代表每個孩子都會有相同結果。請依孩子個性、家庭時間與預算自行評估。</div>
      <div class="article-body"><slot /></div>
    </article>
    <aside class="article-sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-box sticky-box">
        <h2>文章導覽</h2>
        <p>長文建議加入清楚的二級標題，讀者可以快速掃描內容。</p>
        <a href="/blog">回到文章總覽</a>
        <a href="/trial-guide">試聽前必看</a>
        <a href="/resources">免費英文資源</a>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
